        * tests/TCVN-snippet.UTF-8: New file.
        * tests/Makefile.in (check): Check combining behaviour of CP1255,
          CP1258, TCVN.
        * tests/Makefile.msvc (check): Likewise.
        * tests/Makefile.os2 (check): Likewise.

